{"tid":1532261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔中學校長疑開車撞學生 及後要求防暴到場","createTime":"2019-09-02T13:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T18:28:03.000Z","uid":22556,"like":240,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":115,"replies":[{"pid":"688afe1efe2d3e4a9dd99937489054f5b1d724e3","tid":1532261,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:06:51.000Z","msg":"大埔富善邨孔教學院大成何郭佩珍中學，今早約有100名參與罷課的學生，被校方下令要留在校內演講廳內。網上流傳一段錄音，一名女士指，將會將罷課名單交予教育局，該名女士被懷疑是學校校長梁秋雲。下午1時起，有人聚集在校門外，要求校長交代事件及解釋。校方曾派員表示，不會將學生名單交予教育局。<br />\n<br />\n傍晚7時許，校方與學生及校友代表進行閉門對話後，在校外聚集的人群仍不願散去，人數更越來越多，要求與校長公開對話。<br />\n<br />\n校長梁秋雲座駕離開學校時，有示威者設路障阻擋車輛前進，座駕終駛回學校範圍。多名持防暴裝備警員其後到場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/937653736578036?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F366243453719070%2Fposts%2F937653736578036%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1aj%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=51e7ebf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/937653736578036?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"bd0883b6648968052aa9b337c2c6c4e979737047","tid":1532261,"uid":228995,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:07:32.000Z","msg":"殺人犯"},{"pid":"36efc51ab660b3ca571c1ff94a1177f1e4dc7efa","tid":1532261,"uid":258566,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:08:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b93457a74b1f788397b962abb84e2f06ba7bed2","tid":1532261,"uid":258566,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:08:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84a09f82f9a793903a927e875d3418aed0c949a8","tid":1532261,"uid":258566,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:08:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9e5d870f5fefe8f1c59430f55b638780a6f425a","tid":1532261,"uid":26770,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"香港孔教絕大部分係共奴"},{"pid":"960ef5f5bf13359a674f2be4f221f924dd4